task.summary: Default task
Initial commit
Added code snippet to show how to open url in web browser.

XML parser added
InfoWindow for displaying detailed information about resource added
Added HTML formatter for resources.
Fixed bug with layout of info window - now centred on map view.

Added 'resources with any' and 'resources with all' options for user selection
Added missing method specifications.
Added tests to cover methods added to Resource, ResourceRegistry and SelectionState classes.

Added JSON parser and corresponding data.
Added copy of tests in tests.faculty.model (for use on webCAT)
Added JXMapViewer2 license and corresponding GNU GPL v3 license.
Added data files for testing exceptional cases. Completed tests of XML and JSON parsers (for use on webCAT).
Refactored package names
Added more tests to deal with number format exceptions

Added more specific documentation for IResourceParser.parse
Modified specification of IResourceParser.parse so that it now throws IOException in addition to ResourceParserException and modified tests accordingly.
Modified UI to handle IOException.
Added TA NOTE markers so TAs can easily find code related to tasks in the lab.
Removed code that students must add. Replaced model package with obfuscated jar file. Added TODOs to methods that students must complete.
Added TextDeliverables file
Updated to Java 1.8 & IntelliJ 15
Moved libraries from libs to lib
Deleted old libs directory and java-json
Initialized StringBuilder in startElement so app will run from the get-go
Removed json data files. Removed references to JSON from comments.
Modified use of StringBuilder to be consistent with code in demo SAXParserExample
Undid change to StringBuilder
